task_name: Cut Fabric
Cut Velcro
Sew flag on panel
Hem short edge
Sew hook velcro
Sew the panel together along the long sides
Turn inside out
Sew the 2 long sides of the connector Strap  panel
Sew the connector strap to the small Velcro pocket, add the loop Velcro.
Close the sides of the small Velcro pocket.
Cut threads, Turn right side out, Cut corners
Hem one short side
Fold to the marking, and close both sides
Add stitching to the lower corners to create volume
Turn right side out
Add straight single-stitching to the top of the pocket
Sew the center stitch
Add the bartack to the top of the hanging big pocket
Stitch the connector strap to the large pocket
Sew the zipper onto the left panel with USA flag.
Sew the zipper with hemming foot onto the right panel without the flag
Cut extra material off add the zipper pull
Add stitch to both zipper ends
Sew the long sides closed
Sew front panel with pockets to zipper panel
Sew on the side panels
Turn right side out
Clean and inspect for any loose threads, missing, flag, ect.
Insert foam piece into the headrest.
Individually bagged into poly bag S-1997 Size: 9 x 24
Pack into cartons
